    public class MatrixOperationsOptimized<T>
extends MatrixOperations<T>
implements FullMatrixWrapper<T>, MinorMatrixNodeFactory<T>
    optimized overlay of matrix operations object. cofactor expansion tree is constructed of optimized (memory allocation reduced) node objects

      • cofactorExpansion

        public T cofactorExpansion(MinorMatrixComputationTask<T> m)
        Laplace algorithm for computation of determinant of square matrix. this version improves efficiency by using a matrix wrapper that maps minor matrices using index mapping. the cofactor removed column is 1 and the mapping object can map each of the rows as removed
        Parameters:
        m - the matrix to use for computation
        Returns:
        computed result
